text: I take my hats off for all help my hubby n l got from them. They help my hub to gain his health n speech and really care for us. My hub 83 n me 80 we are well looked after in health food n a lot of entertainment n sight seeing at this age. So caring n show so much of love. We both are very proud to be member of them.
I had a staff who is a volunteer of this program, pretty interesting idea to help the local community break the poverty loop
Great place for the community (families and elderly) to hang out and make friends.
Very good help for people need help.
